title: Pet Shop Boys on BBC Radio 1 - July 1992
description: The Pet Shop Boys did a two hour broadcast on Radio 1 each day between 27th and 31st July 1992 whilst Simon Bates was on holiday. The first was the 'Golden Hour' where they played old hits for listeners to guess the year. Secondly, they played an hour of their choice of music including a 15 minute guest megamix by DJs such as the Rap Pack, Dave Seaman and Sasha.
